Package org.forgerock.openam.sm.datalayer.impl.tasks

Class TaskFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.sm.datalayer.impl.tasks.TaskFactory
  • public class TaskFactory
extends Object
    Generates instances of specific Task implementations. Tasks are processed asynchronously by the TaskProcessor.
    See Also:
    Task, SeriesTaskExecutorThread
